snippet.title: Under the Jolly Roger - launch trailer
snippet.description: Under the Jolly Roger is an Open World Action RPG filled with dozens of colonies and forts, hundreds of quests, and countless ships to plunder. You have the ultimate ability to free roam three vast worlds. Preorder Under the Jolly Roger now: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/under-the-jolly-roger/9N8RQZZ6GRCQ?activetab=pivot:overviewtab
